    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Dragon Puncher</strong> is a single-player arcade-style action game designed to be a training tool for Street Fighter and 2D fighting game enthusiasts, and a well-rounded short game. About 15-20 minutes in length, players typically perform 50-75 dragon punch moves per play-through.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026300/extras/68840f534bfb280bfb0abaac16ab6103.poster.avif?t=1769377249\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026300/extras/68840f534bfb280bfb0abaac16ab6103.webm?t=1769377249\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026300/extras/68840f534bfb280bfb0abaac16ab6103.mp4?t=1769377249\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Unleash Your Inner Fighter with Dragon Puncher!</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Arcade-Style Action: Engage in fast-paced, single-player gameplay that captures the essence of classic arcade fighters.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026300/extras/e8b170b1ad1dd9ee27a2c20effea843e.poster.avif?t=1769377249\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026300/extras/e8b170b1ad1dd9ee27a2c20effea843e.webm?t=1769377249\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026300/extras/e8b170b1ad1dd9ee27a2c20effea843e.mp4?t=1769377249\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Perfect Your Moves: Designed as a training tool for Street Fighter and 2D fighting game enthusiasts, it's ideal for honing your dragon punch techniques.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026300/extras/7ef2e27390d0537cafc2b32465f4054b.poster.avif?t=1769377249\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026300/extras/7ef2e27390d0537cafc2b32465f4054b.webm?t=1769377249\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026300/extras/7ef2e27390d0537cafc2b32465f4054b.mp4?t=1769377249\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Quick, Intense Sessions: Each playthrough lasts about 15-20 minutes, during which you'll execute 50-75 dragon punches, offering a compact yet exhilarating experience.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026300/extras/f7a36ea629e858a386e567410c302587.poster.avif?t=1769377249\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026300/extras/f7a36ea629e858a386e567410c302587.webm?t=1769377249\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026300/extras/f7a36ea629e858a386e567410c302587.mp4?t=1769377249\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Full Controller Support: Enjoy seamless gameplay with full controller compatibility, making every move feel natural and responsive.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026300/extras/0aec21a1cd0de05829ce338a686cd0c4.poster.avif?t=1769377249\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026300/extras/0aec21a1cd0de05829ce338a686cd0c4.webm?t=1769377249\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3026300/extras/0aec21a1cd0de05829ce338a686cd0c4.mp4?t=1769377249\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Coming Soon: Stay tuned for the official release and get ready to punch your way to victory!</p></li></ul>",
